 a + x = 3p + \delta\,,\quad x = 0, 2, 4\,,\quad p,\delta \in {\mathbb Z}\,,\quad \delta = 0,1,2 
 \begin{array}{} \delta = 0 & \imp & x = 0\,, & 3 | a  \\ \delta = 1 & \imp & x = 4\,, & 3 | \pars{a + 4}  \\ \delta = 2 & \imp & x = 2\,, & 3 | \pars{a + 2} \end{array} 
